      <title>Cinven 表示正在洽谈收购 Bridgepoint 维生素井的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/cinven-said-in-talks-to-buy-stake-in-bridgepoint-s-vitamin-well</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Cinven 目前正在就收购 Vitamin Well Group 的股份进行深入谈判，该交易对这家瑞典健康饮料制造商的估值超过 20 亿欧元（22 亿美元）。]]></description>
