    <item>
      <title>泰国计划成立金融机构改善服务吸引资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/thailand-plans-finance-agency-to-improve-services-attract-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国表示，将建立一个一站式综合金融服务机构，以增强吸引外国资金和投资者的竞争力，并将很快起草一项法律，帮助该国定位为区域金融中心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/thailand-plans-finance-agency-to-improve-services-attract-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 09:36:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Capitec 称银行系统在全球中断后已恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/capitec-of-south-africa-says-its-systems-hit-by-global-outage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非客户数量最多的银行 Capitec 银行控股有限公司 (Capitec Bank Holdings Ltd.) 表示，在全球大规模计算机故障导致全球航空公司和银行业务中断数小时后，该行已成功恢复所有银行服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/capitec-of-south-africa-says-its-systems-hit-by-global-outage</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 07:49:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韦丹塔斥资 2.46 亿美元夺回赞比亚铜矿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/vedanta-gets-back-zambia-copper-mines-after-paying-246-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大约五年后，韦丹塔资源有限公司向债权人支付了约 2.46 亿美元，重新获得了赞比亚孔科拉铜矿的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/vedanta-gets-back-zambia-copper-mines-after-paying-246-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 03:54:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国全国人大三次会议结果令人失望，铜价或创 2022 年以来最差一周</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/copper-set-for-worst-week-since-2022-as-china-plenum-disappoints</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国政策会议未能提出更多刺激措施来支撑金属需求，铜价创下 2022 年以来最大单周跌幅，铁矿石价格延续跌势，跌向每吨 100 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/copper-set-for-worst-week-since-2022-as-china-plenum-disappoints</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 03:09:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员评估技术故障影响，油价窄幅波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-19</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商权衡全球技术故障造成的影响，油价在窄幅区间波动，此次故障已给银行、航空公司等众多企业带来困扰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-19</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 23:24:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
