    <item>
      <title>夏威夷电力公司等多家公司参与了价值 40 亿美元的毛伊岛火灾救援行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/hawaiian-electric-among-firms-eyeing-4-billion-maui-fire-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，夏威夷电力工业公司 (Hawaiian Electric Industries Inc.) 是暂时同意支付逾 40 亿美元以解决数百起有关去年席卷毛伊岛的山火的诉讼的公司之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/hawaiian-electric-among-firms-eyeing-4-billion-maui-fire-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 21:04:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>远洋集团债务计划获支持，但仍面临阻力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/sino-ocean-says-some-lenders-back-debt-restructuring-proposal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[违约的建筑商远洋集团控股有限公司正在努力争取足够的支持，以使其债务重组计划获得批准，但由于主要债券持有人团体的反对，仍远远未达到所需的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/sino-ocean-says-some-lenders-back-debt-restructuring-proposal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 17:10:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国被指囤积运往捷克的天然气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/germany-accused-of-hoarding-gas-meant-to-supply-czech-republic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克共和国指责德国在该地区努力寻找俄罗斯天然气替代供应之际，通过削减出口管道的容量来囤积天然气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/germany-accused-of-hoarding-gas-meant-to-supply-czech-republic</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 14:36:53 GMT</pubDate>
